# Web app environment (Vite). Copy to `.env.local` for local overrides; only
# VITE_-prefixed vars are exposed to the client. Real values are not committed.

# Base URL of the Khiimori API. Optional locally — when unset the app falls back
# to http://localhost:8080 (see src/lib/api.ts). In production this is injected
# at build time by the CI deploy job (the Cloud Run service URL); there is no
# hardcoded production URL in the source.
VITE_API_BASE_URL=http://localhost:8080
